{"tid":1506874,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"琴日究竟深水埗站發生咩事?完全無人講","createTime":"2019-08-26T02:48:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T03:15:21.000Z","uid":137217,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"000e217f0b9f865cdef5e5287424ca25ee258f26","tid":1506874,"uid":137217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:48:13.000Z","msg":"琴日我一出地鐵<br />\n就見到成班示威者塞咗係條電梯度<br />\n果下我覺得怪,因為唔係話去黃大仙架咩<br />\n跟住2秒唔夠就聽到上面有槍聲(大堂傳嚟)<br />\n跟住就聞到應該係胡椒彈既味<br />\n跟住成班兄弟即刻係電梯衝返落月台<br />\n我當時係普通市民look無gear<br />\n又帶緊con,驚班癲狗係月台放tg<br />\n所以我即刻上返架地鐵<br />\n係長沙灣落就見到一班記者企咗係度等緊<br />\n但今日完全無新聞又無post又無相<br />\n究竟係點"},{"pid":"8f6b1c1cbc85951fa2d5ac666d40a142333746a1","tid":1506874,"uid":137217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:57:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3465f01ce202769e8bcc8244a27734dd39480c9f","tid":1506874,"uid":145254,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:58:14.000Z","msg":"下次你出去行下咪知咩事"},{"pid":"6de523fa8c1b9e68e01870cd44c0ab8a10e946a1","tid":1506874,"uid":137217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3465f01ce202769e8bcc8244a27734dd39480c9f","tid":1506874,"uid":145254,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:58:14.000Z","msg":"下次你出去行下咪知咩事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:13:43.000Z","msg":"廢話可以講少兩句"},{"pid":"e677bf49112d27af566da03d0738e8b2726711fc","tid":1506874,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:13:55.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1<br />\n時間: 13:00<br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 文宣集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505474</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogleDrive: 91機場文宣資源 (手足有新貨話我知，會Upload上去)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=3a39